OL,3,CThe kayakers paddling for plastic in
OL,4,Chard to reach places
OL,6,FA tiny, deserted cove with views of
OL,7,FDevon's rolling hills might sound like
OL,8,Fan idyllic place to spend a morning.
OL,10,FBut if you look a little closer,
OL,11,Fthings at Kingsbridge Estuary are not
OL,12,Fas perfect as they first seem.
OL,14,FOld toothbrushes, coat hangers,
OL,15,Flighters and used fishing gear litter
OL,16,Fthe coastline. And, despite being far
OL,17,Ffrom any cafes and only accessible via
OL,18,Fkayak, coffee cups are strewn across
OL,19,Fits shingles.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
