OL,3,CThe kayakers paddling for plastic in
OL,4,Chard to reach places
OL,6,FIt has now started to 'Paddle for
OL,7,FPlastics' - using kayaks to remove
OL,8,Ftonnes of litter from parts of the
OL,9,Fcoast that are otherwise impossible to
OL,10,Freach.
OL,12,F"It came about quite naturally as we
OL,13,Fwere finding all this plastic,"
OL,14,FClaire, from Odyssey, told ITV News.
OL,16,F"We realised there were a lot of coves
OL,17,Fthat you can't access by walking, so
OL,18,Fyou have to access them another way.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
