OL,3,CThe kayakers paddling for plastic in
OL,4,Chard to reach places
OL,6,F"Even with a boat, you sometimes can't
OL,7,Fpull up onto shallow shores. So we
OL,8,Frealised kayaks would be perfect
OL,9,Fbecause you can pull up anywhere and
OL,10,Ftake plastic away on them."
OL,12,FThe group find all kinds of plastic
OL,13,Fwaste, but ropes, nets, polystrene,
OL,14,Fplastic bottle tops and cans are the
OL,15,Fmost common.
OL,17,F"Anything plastic you can think of, I
OL,18,Ffeel like we've found," Claire said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
