OL,3,CThe kayakers paddling for plastic in
OL,4,Chard to reach places
OL,6,FOdyssey has so far collected 22 tonnes
OL,7,Fof plastic and other waste from the
OL,8,FSouth Devon Coast using its kayaks.
OL,10,FThe items are then repurposed - with
OL,11,Fsome of it even being used to create
OL,12,Fnew kayaks which can be used to remove
OL,13,Fmore litter.
OL,15,F"It's quite special that it's fully
OL,16,Fcircular," Claire said. "It also helps
OL,17,Flots of community groups across the
OL,18,FSouth West to help them get to harder
OL,19,Fto reach places.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
